{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "演繹文明", "storyInfo": "萊托試圖說服掌握著自救軍情報的戈爾丁投向城防軍。變形者接近戈爾丁，Logos追著變形者而來，與變形者借戲對談。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來這裡做什麼？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我說的那樣，只是來看一場演出。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......孩子們，都到我身後來。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#3$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托中校，無意冒犯，但這裡不歡迎你。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不用這麼生分吧，戈爾丁。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#10$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一向認同你的努力，越是艱難的時代，教育的重要性就越應該被凸顯出來。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中校先生，您這麼說，好像自己和這個“艱難的時代”沒什麼關係似的。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管什麼時代，您穿得可總是十足體面。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您胸前的勳章也越來越多了。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "協助軍事委員會管理倫蒂尼姆不是一件輕鬆的事情，我也遇到了很多......困難。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我對這座城市的熱愛始終未曾改變，就這點而言，我和你們一樣。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鞋匠湯姆肯定很贊同。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "湯姆也是我的朋友，發生那樣的事我並不樂意見到。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是喝醉了酒，嘟囔“陛下”和“蒸汽騎士”什麼的，他甚至不怎麼會拼“薩卡茲”。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還活著。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們存在的意義不只是活著。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想指控我為維多利亞的叛徒嗎，戈爾丁？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士們，我敬佩你們的勇氣。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你們誤會了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我今天來這裡，只是想再看一看這所學校罷了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉小姐，很遺憾，看來你已經忘記我了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......忘記？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡度過的時間不比你少，茉莉小姐。我甚至還記得你和同你一起來的那批孩子。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，軍校畢業後，我的閒置時間就沒有那麼多了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可戈爾丁，你曾是信任我的。我們時常一起談論高盧的歷史，聊起那些不朽的文學——", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#10$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，萊托中校。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我十分感謝你的父親，他多年來一直資助著這所學校，他試圖為孩子們點燃智慧的火炬，驅散蒙昧與混沌。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾以為你是和他一樣的人......而你，卻親手熄滅了那點本就微弱的火光。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？戈爾丁，那你覺得，這所學校為什麼能維持到今天？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——你別想威脅我們！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有威脅各位的理由和動機，孩子們還在呢。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，我們都是高盧遺民。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道，戰爭是最無情的毀滅者，除了帶走成千上萬的生命，還會摧毀人類為通向智識做出的一切努力。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想看見倫蒂尼姆變成下一個林貢斯，也不想讓剛才看到的如此美好的戲劇演出就此絕跡。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我為我自己選擇的責任。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我無法贊同你的看法。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林貢斯的皇家歌劇院已經化作灰燼，而《凱旋頌》仍在各時各地被反復演繹。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建築會倒塌，巨構會瓦解，但我們曾凝集其中的結晶卻永不會消亡。那是我們的教育、我們的文化、我們的希望。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭的陰雲越是濃烈，我們就越是需要堅持信念，需要相信美的東西，來提醒自己身為人類與野獸的差別。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你相信這種對抗能贏？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們所代表的那些東西，恐懼、權力、殺戮......永遠無法馴化每一個人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須相信。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只能相信。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有光，我們就會向光而行。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我羡慕你，戈爾丁女士。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看頭頂的陰雲吧，暴風雨就快來了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在落雷之前，我們都還有時間，我們都還有選擇。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望有一天......我能看到這齣戲的結尾。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g1_lentiavenue", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開學校之後，城防軍指揮官並未在街上停留。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的確是一個人來的，並沒有更多城防軍官兵來到附近。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她必須找到亞當斯，將消息傳出去。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管那位指揮官表現得多麼沒有敵意，他都不會無緣無故地找上他們學校。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉不知道，孩子們不知道，可是戈爾丁知道他為什麼會來。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼突然這麼多薩卡茲？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通往書店的路很熟悉，她在過去兩年多的時間裡走了無數回。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可今天這條路突然變得很長，長到一眼望不到頭，她又想到了薩卡茲進城的那一天。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她真的能夠改變嗎？"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須相信，我必須......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁突然感覺到自己被一種恐懼扼住了咽喉。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她簡直要吐出來了，她轉身逃離。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘭西，帕蒂！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些孩子......！蘭——", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......或許這樣簡單的任務並不值得勞您大駕，閣下。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的話，你應該選擇把戈爾丁女士抓起來，萊托。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德就會這麼做。換作老紅眼病的話，整座學校都不會剩下一個活口。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，我們知道你不是薩卡茲。你還想著給自己，給城防軍，給這座城市裡的居民留一點最後的體面。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們相信這樣會更保險。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘭西，帕蒂......不知道孩子們有沒有危險。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中校先生，我很害怕。我既害怕像您這樣的人和薩卡茲傷害孩子們，也害怕......孩子們變成像您一樣的人。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您的語氣和這位昏迷的女士一模一樣。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#4$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我們在感受。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她關心那些年幼的維多利亞人，勝過關心自己。我們能感受到，卻很難理解。尤其這種關心還不是基於血緣。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......閣下？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們對你們很感興趣。透過你們，我們能更好地理解自己......理解薩卡茲。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您想從我們身上找尋一些答案？關於......什麼的答案？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托，你並不像那種對薩卡茲感到好奇的人。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，閣下。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#5$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任務是第一優先的。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把這位茉莉小姐帶回去吧，中校先生。看好她。我們會留在戈爾丁女士身邊，為接下來的戰爭取得更多情報。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，閣下。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#5$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，閣下？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人發現我們了。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是否需要我讓更多士兵過來？", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了，士兵們攔不住他。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他從特蕾西婭那裡學到了不少。我們也許很快就能......輕鬆地聊聊天。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......茉莉。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我出去的這段時間，沒出什麼事吧？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，蘭西和帕蒂嚇壞了，拉爾夫那幾個大孩子帶著小傢伙們休息去了。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。我在想......孩子們會喜歡這些戲的吧？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的努力是有意義的，對吧？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在說什麼？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......沒什麼。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不用在意那個城防軍指揮官的話，戈爾丁女士。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，我不是很舒服，我想休息一下。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，茉莉，這裡就麻煩你收拾了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這齣戲該有一個結尾的，蒸汽騎士已經走到王宮門前了。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過幾天，孩子們會把最後一幕演完的，對嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一定。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個故事的結尾只要沒被演繹，就總是有很多種可能性的。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，已經上演的戲，也未必無法改變，人們總是想看到更新鮮的版本。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在一旁看了很久了，是吧？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然舞台還在，我們能不能重新演一遍呢？從第一幕開始。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都總是在幻想，如果一切沒有發生會怎樣。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推演沒有意義。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果只是些渺茫的可能性......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好先生，若您正好閒來無事，不如加入這場演出吧？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "x": 0.0, "y": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早安，閣下！您的臉上佈滿愁容，請問是什麼讓您如此心焦？", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勝利的號角聲已在城牆上盤旋了三天三夜，可我的心為何還是如此焦灼？", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們偉大的將軍不是早已凱旋了嗎？讚美他的英勇與無畏！", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英勇？無畏？也許是的。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次激進的號召，將我們的信念凝成一團。代價，卻是近在眼前的毀滅和仇恨。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本該侍奉一位君主，卻將你的忠誠獻給了一位賊人。", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "y": 100.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.5, "yScaleTo": 1.5, "yfrom": 100.0, "yTo": 80.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台上，神秘的觀眾向前一步，視線從眼前人的身上移向了遠方。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他並非在醞釀情緒，相反，他在整理那些早已塵封的關於另一處戰場的往事。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "x": 0.0, "y": 150.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.15, "yScaleTo": 1.15, "xfrom": 0.0, "yfrom": 150.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 150.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我追隨的並非君主，而是一種正直，一股勇氣。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再往前走的話，迎接你的只有毀滅。", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活著看到這個國家被暴君帶著走向毀滅，遠比個體毀滅更可怕。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎知她的結局，閣下？", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能預見她的結局，正如我知曉她的來路。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡說！你尚年幼，怎敢張口懷念往昔？", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能令太陽永不下落？生出這種欲望本就是最大的貪婪。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了維繫這盛大的光輝，我見過無數瘋狂之舉。他們或是化身強盜，或是相互爭鬥，最終只會加速這個國家的腐朽。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "x": 290.0, "y": 80.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.5, "yScaleTo": 1.5, "xfrom": 290.0, "yfrom": 80.0, "xTo": 250.0, "yTo": 80.0, "duration": 10.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“茉莉”在舞台上轉了個身，輕踱幾步，再回過身，將面目隱藏在燈光下的陰影裡。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但另一位演員先開口了，他神色沉靜如水，微微側手，又將雙手交叉。"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "x": 0.0, "y": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i02", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "xfrom": 0.0, "yfrom": 150.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 15.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不願承認，下墜之人想要攀住日光，握在手中的卻只可能是閃電。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道人們就只能甘願墜落？", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們也可以選擇不再回望山巔。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假使他們掉轉自己的視線，他們會發現面前的深淵不是深淵，而是包含無窮可能性的沃土。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深淵可被戰勝？你並不清楚深淵的真相，也未必知曉，時間緊迫。", "name": "“茉莉”"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深淵就在身前，我等可用肉身填於深淵，用鮮血燒盡殘垣，給後人留下一片廣闊原野。", "name": "“神秘觀眾”"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.9, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只有等到舊日的灰燼全部被吹散，原野上才能長出新的糧食，來餵飽我們的下一代。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}